description.displayText: Judith is an outstanding caregiver! My children really enjoy time spent with her. She is extremely responsible, well educated, compassionate, and an overall asset! I would recommend Judith highly and trust that you will be more than happy with what she has to offer.
description.originalText: Judith is an outstanding caregiver! My children really enjoy time spent with her. She is extremely responsible, well educated, compassionate, and an overall asset! I would recommend Judith highly and trust that you will be more than happy with what she has to offer.

description.displayText:
Judith always displayed a great amount of care for our son and he responded fondly. Judith was always a responsive caregiver, sharing her ideas on R's care but always deferring to our preferences. She took the time to begin teaching our son sign language and, despite his young age, we have seen him begin to respond to those teachings.  

Judith is a very likeable young lady who earnestly wants the best for our son. We have appreciated her judgment as well as her kind nature.
